{
  "stem": "7177.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was very little to describe, because there were the German soldiers marching through your little town.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But actually, we had known already from the day before, because there were a lot of Dutch people who would work in Germany, right across the border.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they came home and they would say, oh, tomorrow is going to invasion, because they told us so.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we actually knew the day before.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there was nothing that you could do about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "OK?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By that time, 1940, my older brother, Jos-- because of his very, very good schooling and the things that he had had, he had been eligible for a position in the Dutch army.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was a second lieutenant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember that he made a phone call to the house and warned us to be careful.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there wasn't anything that he could do either.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that's one of the things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I know that, that I remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They marched into town and through town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Through town.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Did not remain there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was one battalion that came, I think, maybe two weeks later, and stayed there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was not the very day of the occupation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The occupation started, and they had to fight their way into Germany-- or into Holland-- excuse me-- to, you know, get as far as possible.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
